        <obo:IAO_0000111>in-situ hybridization assay</obo:IAO_0000111>
        <obo:IAO_0000112>Use of in situ hybridization to examine gene expression in the embryonic, neonatal, and adult urogenital system. PMID:22639265</obo:IAO_0000112>
