        <obo:IAO_0000111>lavage fluid specimen</obo:IAO_0000111>
        <obo:IAO_0000112>The collection of bronchoalveolar lavage fluid (BAL) from the lungs of mice in order to study the cytokines present.</obo:IAO_0000112>
