        <obo:IAO_0000117>Philippe Rocca-Serra</obo:IAO_0000117>
        <obo:IAO_0000119>adapted from wikipedia [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nucleic_acid_hybridization]</obo:IAO_0000119>
        <obo:OBI_0001847>hybridization assay</obo:OBI_0001847>
