Isolation of proliferation factor of immature T-cell clone in concanavalin A-stimulated splenocyte culture supernatant. Immunology. 2003 Jun;109(2):209-16. PMID: 12757615</obo:IAO_0000112>
        <obo:IAO_0000114 rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000120"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115 xml:lang="en">Supernatant of a cell culture is a material entity which contains media, supplements, and secreted products of the cells and becomes the environment of cultivated cell.</obo:IAO_0000115>
